<h3 id="customizing-responses">Customizing responses</h3>
<p>You can create more custom data structures by using aliases.<br />
Here, <code>viewer</code> becomes <code>me</code>, <code>name</code> becomes <code>fullname</code> and <code>avatarURL</code> becomes <code>picture</code>.</p>

<div class="card card-code text-white bg-dark border-dark">
  
